author: Nerdstalgic
description:
Long before Zack Snyder shaped the DCEU, Mad Max visionary George Miller was days away from launching an entirely different DC Universe. With a full cast, completed costumes, and production set to begin, Justice League: Mortal was primed to be the first big-screen team-up of DC’s biggest heroes.

So what happened?

This is the story of the Justice League movie we almost got… and why it never happened.

#justiceleague #superman #dceu #zacksnyder #georgemiller
title: Justice League Was Almost VERY Different
